FAISALABAD, Aug 10 (APP):Police arrested two drug peddlers with 40-kg hashish near Chiniot  Bazaar on Thursday.
Police said Lyallpur Town police arrested two accused in Chiniot Bazaar. Policeseized about 40-kg of hashish from their possession.They were identified as Maqsood Ahmed and Majid.
